1972;;Boxcar Bertha;;American;;Martin Scorsese;;Barbara Hershey, David Carradine, Barry Primus, John Carradine, Bernie Casey;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boxcar_Bertha;;The film tells the story of Boxcar Bertha Thompson and "Big" Bill Shelly, two train robbers and lovers who are caught up in the plight of railroad workers in the American South. When Bertha is implicated in the murder of a wealthy gambler, the pair become fugitives.